---
import LayoutB from '../../layouts/LayoutB.astro';
---
<LayoutB title="Subtle Somatics — Ethereal Depth" description="Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics with Kaja Possert-Bienzle.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"><img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="" /><div class="hero-overlay"></div></div>
    <div class="hero-content text-center">
      <p class="hero-pre">I'm inviting you&hellip;</p>
      <h1><em>to align</em> with the free-flowing<br/>rhythm of your essence</h1>
      <div class="hero-divider"></div>
      <p class="hero-sub"><em>to unfold</em> the luminous wonder of deeper aliveness<br/><em>to embody</em> the radiant expression of your unique creativity, love and power</p>
      <a href="#connect" class="btn btn-gold">Begin Your Journey</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section text-center">
    <p class="gold-line">Subtle Somatics</p>
    <h2 style="margin:0 auto 2rem; max-width:700px">What if everything we need is already here?</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 auto; color:var(--text-light)">This work is not about fixing or striving. It's about entering the field where what's true begins to reveal itself, in its own rhythm and time.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section class="about-section" id="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-img-wrap"><img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja" /><div class="about-img-border"></div></div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="gold-line">Kaja Possert-Bienzle</p>
        <h2>Unfolding companion.<br/>Wholeness witnesser.<br/>Integration facilitator.</h2>
        <p>I work with the natural intelligence of your body-mind-soul system — where sensations begin to speak, energy reorganises from the depth, and something deeply resonant in you starts moving through silent presence.</p>
        <p class="about-purpose"><em>"Container schaffen, in denen die nächsten Generationen gut begleitet werden können."</em></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Offerings -->
  <section class="offerings-section" id="offerings">
    <div class="offerings-inner">
      <p class="gold-line text-center">Offerings</p>
      <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:4rem">Two gateways into your innate wholeness</h2>

      <div class="offering">
        <div class="offering-visual"><img src="/images/subtle-coaching.png" alt="Subtle Coaching" /><div class="offering-glow"></div></div>
        <div class="offering-text">
          <h3>Subtle Coaching</h3>
          <p class="offering-lead">Meet yourself where you are — at the depth where you are vastly resourced to be with life's complexity.</p>
          <p>In presence-based coaching, we work with the alive, moment-to-moment experience of your body-mind-soul system. Through deepening self-contact and gentle inquiry, qualities like courage, tenderness, clarity, and inner strength emerge — not as something new, but as something that was always there.</p>
          <a href="#connect" class="btn">Explore</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="offering reverse">
        <div class="offering-visual"><img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" /><div class="offering-glow"></div></div>
        <div class="offering-text">
          <h3>Spinal Energetics</h3>
          <p class="offering-lead">Experience profound mind-body-soul connection — supported by subtle-and-powerful touch and sound.</p>
          <p>Working with the spine as a gateway to your energetic, emotional, and physical layers. Through subtle touch, combined with sound and presence, the body's own intelligence is invited to reorganise, release, and integrate. Many experience deep states of warmth and aliveness.</p>
          <a href="#connect" class="btn">Explore</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pillars -->
  <section class="pillars-section">
    <div class="pillars-inner">
      <div class="p-card">
        <span class="p-accent">I</span>
        <h3>An encounter</h3>
        <p>Truly getting to know the thoughts, emotions and sensations you have moment to moment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-divider"></div>
      <div class="p-card">
        <span class="p-accent">II</span>
        <h3>An unfolding</h3>
        <p>Experiencing your vast inner resourcefulness — strength, love, presence and more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-divider"></div>
      <div class="p-card">
        <span class="p-accent">III</span>
        <h3>An integration</h3>
        <p>Connecting into deeper coherence, alignment and embodiment of your innate wholeness.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="values-row">
      <div class="val"><h4>Presence</h4><p>Being fully here — with what is.</p></div>
      <div class="val"><h4>Wholeness</h4><p>You are already whole.</p></div>
      <div class="val"><h4>Embodiment</h4><p>The tissues, the breath, the bones.</p></div>
      <div class="val"><h4>Trust</h4><p>An intelligence that knows the way.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Image -->
  <section class="img-break"><img src="/images/kaja-secondary.png" alt="" /><div class="img-break-ov"></div></section>

  <!-- Connect -->
  <section class="section" id="connect">
    <div class="connect-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="gold-line">Connect</p>
        <h2>Your next step</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">Begin with a free discovery call — a conversation to sense into whether this work resonates with you.</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a></p>
        <p style="color:var(--text-dim); font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:0.5rem">Online & in person — Vienna / Styria, Austria</p>
      </div>
      <form class="c-form" action="#">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Your name" />
        <input type="email" placeholder="Your email *" required />
        <textarea rows="5" placeholder="What's calling you?" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">Send</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutB>

<style>
  .hero { position:relative; min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; overflow:hidden; }
  .hero-bg { position:absolute; inset:0; }
  .hero-bg img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; filter:brightness(0.4); }
  .hero-overlay { position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(13,8,32,0.5), rgba(13,8,32,0.8)); }
  .hero-content { position:relative; z-index:1; max-width:800px; padding:2rem; margin-top:3rem; }
  .hero-pre { font-family:var(--font-h); font-size:1.3rem; font-style:italic; color:var(--text-light); margin-bottom:2rem; }
  .hero h1 { margin-bottom:2rem; }
  .hero h1 em { color:var(--gold); font-weight:400; }
  .hero-divider { width:60px; height:1px; background:var(--gold-dim); margin:2rem auto; }
  .hero-sub { font-family:var(--font-h); font-size:1.2rem; color:var(--text-light); line-height:2; margin-bottom:3rem; max-width:none; }
  .hero-sub em { color:var(--gold); }

  .gold-line { font-size:0.75rem; letter-spacing:0.2em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:1rem; }

  .about-section { padding:7rem 2rem; background:var(--deep); }
  .about-inner { max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1.4fr; gap:5rem; align-items:center; }
  .about-img-wrap { position:relative; }
  .about-img-wrap img { border-radius:2px; position:relative; z-index:1; }
  .about-img-border { position:absolute; top:12px; left:12px; right:-12px; bottom:-12px; border:1px solid var(--gold-dim); border-radius:2px; }
  .about-text h2 { margin-bottom:1.5rem; line-height:1.3; }
  .about-text p { color:var(--text-light); margin-bottom:1.2rem; }
  .about-purpose { color:var(--gold); font-family:var(--font-h); font-size:1rem; margin-top:1rem; }

  .offerings-section { padding:7rem 2rem; }
  .offerings-inner { max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; }
  .offering { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1.3fr; gap:4rem; align-items:center; margin-bottom:5rem; }
  .offering.reverse { grid-template-columns:1.3fr 1fr; }
  .offering.reverse .offering-visual { order:2; }
  .offering-visual { position:relative; }
  .offering-visual img { border-radius:2px; width:100%; }
  .offering-glow { position:absolute; inset:-20px; background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(45,27,105,0.3), transparent 70%); z-index:-1; }
  .offering-text h3 { color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:1rem; font-size:1.8rem; }
  .offering-lead { color:var(--cream); font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .offering-text p { color:var(--text-light); margin-bottom:1.2rem; font-size:0.95rem; }
  .offering-text .btn { margin-top:0.5rem; }

  .pillars-section { padding:5rem 2rem; background:var(--deep); }
  .pillars-inner { max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:2rem; }
  .p-card { flex:1; text-align:center; padding:2rem 1.5rem; }
  .p-accent { font-family:var(--font-h); font-size:1.8rem; color:var(--gold-dim); display:block; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .p-card h3 { color:var(--cream); font-style:italic; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .p-card p { color:var(--text-dim); font-size:0.9rem; margin:0 auto; }
  .p-divider { width:1px; height:80px; background:var(--gold-dim); flex-shrink:0; }

  .values-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr); gap:2rem; }
  .val { text-align:center; padding:2rem 1rem; border-top:1px solid var(--gold-dim); }
  .val h4 { font-family:var(--font-h); font-style:italic; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:0.5rem; font-size:1.2rem; }
  .val p { color:var(--text-dim); font-size:0.85rem; margin:0 auto; }

  .img-break { position:relative; height:45vh; overflow:hidden; }
  .img-break img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; filter:brightness(0.5); }
  .img-break-ov { position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--midnight), transparent 30%, transparent 70%, var(--midnight)); }

  .connect-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; align-items:start; }
  .connect-grid h2 { margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .c-form { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1rem; }
  .c-form input, .c-form textarea { padding:0.85rem 1rem; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border:1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.15); color:var(--cream); font-family:var(--font-b); font-size:0.9rem; }
  .c-form input:focus, .c-form textarea:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--gold); }
  .c-form input::placeholder, .c-form textarea::placeholder { color:var(--text-dim); }
  .c-form textarea { resize:vertical; min-height:100px; }

  @media (max-width:768px) {
    .about-inner, .offering, .offering.reverse, .connect-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .offering.reverse .offering-visual { order:0; }
    .pillars-inner { flex-direction:column; }
    .p-divider { width:60px; height:1px; }
    .values-row { grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .img-break { height:30vh; }
  }
</style>
